Validate NAT Instance

1. SSH into your Public Instance from last week

2. Then, from that Public Instance ssh into your Private Instance

3. Your Private Instance should be able to ping 8.8.8.8. 

4. Your Private Instance should be able to "sudo yum install nc" to install netcat from an Internet repo


